<P>
   (NYT1) UNDATED -- Oct. 17, 1999 -- TVGUIDE-BUYER-MEDIA-B&AMP;W,
10-17 -- Dr. Henry Yuen's company, Gemstar International, in buying
TV Guide, will lead the race to provide on-screen program guides.
It is ``the remote control of the next generation of television
viewing,'' says Yuen, who has a doctorate in applied mathematics
and a law degree. (New York Times Photo)
</P>
