<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-18 04:30 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0189 &Cx1f; tab-z
r a BC-HARD-HATS-FOR-GORE-EC     10-18 1013
