<P>
   A profusely illustrated collection of records about
</P>
<P>
   subjects as various as sports and technology.
</P>
<P>
   SUGAR BUSTERS! by H. Leighton Steward et al. ......... 2 ... 2
... 64
</P>
<P>
   (Ballantine, $22.) A diet designed for losing weight,
</P>
<P>
   increasing energy and combating disease. (b)
</P>
<P>
   THE CARBOHYDRATE ADDICT'S HEALTHY HEART PROGRAM, ..... 3 ... _
... 1
</P>
<P>
   by Richard F. Heller, Rachael F. Heller and Frederic
</P>
<P>
   J. Vagnini. (Ballantine, $24.95.) A diet. (b)
</P>
<P>
   LIFE STRATEGIES, by Phillip C. McGraw. (Hyperion. $24.95.) .. 4
.. _ .. 14
</P>
<P>
   How to find what matters in your life and what to do about it.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
