<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-18 09:17 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0303 &Cx1f; var-z
u i BC-R-U.S.-WORLD-ROLE-REV     10-18 1191
