<HEADLINE>
WILT THE STILT'S VIEWS ON RACE AND HOOPS 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (duplication notice: also sent with `s' code)  
 (bl)  
 By TOM KUNTZ   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
