<HEADLINE>
TRIANGULATION: POLITICS' NEW GEOMETRY IS OLD MATH 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (bl)  
 By RICHARD L. BERKE   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   Texas Gov. George W. Bush gets no higher praise from President
