<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-10-18 10:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0390 &Cx1f; tab-z
r l BC-PLANT-BULBS-NOW-LIFEB     10-18 1108
