<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   The UNDATED Fort Worth Star-Telegram story slugged TRIVIA-Q&AMP;A
will not move in tonight's file for clients of the New York Times
News Service. It is scheduled to move on Tuesday. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   nn
</P>
</TEXT>
