 This is the headline  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Systems has a work order / job ticket tracking system called the
AR System (Action Request System). I spoke with Stephen Veneruso
and Vicki Beckvar about the possibility of using that program to
create a separate tracking system for our department. I understand
that it is very customizable and Vicki and Stephen are pros at it.
</P>
<P>
   We would have to buy more licenses. They are sold in blocks of 5
for $10,000.00 each. The licenses are floating which means that the
software can be installed on everyones workstation, but only 5
users can use it at the same time.
</P>
<P>
   I asked Stephen and Vicki about working with them on this and
they were agreeable. Stephen said that it would be mid-February
before they could begin working on it.
