with tonight's airing of ``The Lost Children of Rockdale.'' The
program has been the buzz of Rockdale for weeks among community
leaders, teachers, parents and teens. A community forum is set to
discuss the segment Oct. 26 at the local library. (Stafford,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
