BUSH (Phoenix) - Texas Gov. George Bush returns to Arizona Monday
to make an announcement about his Internet campaign contribution
site and to make a speech on an undisclosed subject, all at the
Phoenician resort. By KRIS MAYES. Story will move in the ``A''
category. &QL;
