visibility for many conditions?
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  This month is Healthy Lung Month. American Lung Association,
1-800-586-4872 or www.lungusa
</P>
<P>
   .org.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  This week is Hepatitis Awareness Week. Hepatitis Foundation
International, 1-800-891-0707 or www.hepfi.org.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  (October 19) Today is National Mammography Day. For local
mammography sites, call the American Cancer Society help line at
404-816-4994.
</P>
<P>
   _Lillian Lee Kim
